        {
          "question": "<p>Write one example for each of the following type of motion.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman;\">\r\n\t<li>Rectilinear</li>\r\n\t<li>Circular</li>\r\n\t<li>Periodic</li>\r\n\t<li>Circular and periodic</li>\r\n</ol>",
          "id": 478200,
          "options_data": [],
          "solution_data": [
            {
              "id": 255927,
              "solution": "<p>The examples of different types of motion are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman;\">\r\n\t<li>Rectilinear - An apple falling vertically downwards.&nbsp;</li>\r\n\t<li>Circular - The motion of a point marked on the hands of a clock.</li>\r\n\t<li>Periodic - The motion of a child on a swing.</li>\r\n\t<li>Circular and periodic - Blades of a rotating fan.</li>\r\n</ol>"
            }
          ],
          "num_solutions_data": [],
          "alternate_solutions_data": [],
          "marks": 0,
