        {
          "question": "<p>Match the events related to motion in Column I with the types of motions given in Column II.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Column I</strong></td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Column II</strong></td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(a) A moving wheel of a&nbsp;sewing machine</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(i) Circular motion</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(b) Movement of tip of the minute hand of a clock in one hour</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(ii) Rotational motion</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(c) A moving swing</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td>(iii) Periodic motion</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>",
