          "question": "<p>Boojho was riding in his bicycle along a straight road. He classified the motion of various parts of the bicycle as</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman;\">\r\n\t<li>rectilinear motion,</li>\r\n\t<li>circular motion and</li>\r\n\t<li>both rectilinear as well as circular motion.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Can you list one part of the bicycle for each type of motion? Support your answer with reason.</p>",
          "id": 480087,
