          "solution_data": [
            {
              "id": 256705,
              "solution": "<ol start=\"1\" style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman;\">\r\n\t<li><strong>Rectilinear motion:</strong> Handlebar or seat of the bicycle has rectilinear motion only. It moves in a straight line as the wheels of the bicycle move forward.</li>\r\n\t<li><strong>Circular motion:</strong> Pedal of the bicycle is having circular motion only as it rotates with its shaft but does not move from its place.</li>\r\n\t<li><strong>Rectilinear and circular motion:</strong>&nbsp;The wheel of the bicycle is having both circular and rectilinear motion. Wheels rotate on their shafts as well as move forward on the ground.</li>\r\n</ol>"
